    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in TCP/IP-based internets.  In particular, it describes managed objects used for managing the Mobile Node, Foreign Agent and Home Agent of the Mobile IP Protocol. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
